<p>To Zyn: You have been there for me and all of us when I was a clueless newbie and you're still here every time I need you as a moderator on the Butterfly squad. I can truly say that you're one of the hardest working and most essential people on this wiki, and you don't hear that nearly often enough. Through your effort, you inspire me and others to do better every day. Thank you. For everything. I'm proud to serve under you, Captain. 07</p>
